          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Downloading stock data from Yahoo Finance...\n",
            "✅ Data downloaded: 250 trading days\n",
            "   From: 2025-05-06  →  To: 2026-05-06\n",
            "\n",
            "Latest closing prices (₹):\n",
            "HDFC Bank       ₹776.60\n",
