        "id": "Fbs0962Y8S1U"
      },
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "## 📉 Section 7 — Volatility Analysis\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Annualised Volatility Formula:**  \n",
        "> `σ_annual = σ_daily × √252`  \n",
        "> Where σ_daily = standard deviation of daily returns  \n",
        "> 252 = number of trading days in a year  \n",
        ">\n",
        "> Higher volatility = higher risk. Lower volatility = more stable returns."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 10,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "sc6qEMVM8S1V",
        "outputId": "aa56f35e-8f43-45c0-bfcc-b401efe0ff82"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Annualised Volatility (%):\n",
            "==============================\n",
            "  HDFC Bank      18.7%  █████████\n",
            "  Reliance       20.1%  ██████████\n",
            "  Infosys        26.2%  █████████████\n",
            "  TCS            22.3%  ███████████\n",
            "  ICICI Bank     18.4%  █████████\n",
            "\n",
            "  Nifty 50     21.1%  (approx portfolio avg)\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "# Annualised volatility\n",
        "ann_volatility = daily_returns.std() * np.sqrt(TRADING_DAYS) * 100\n",
        "\n",
        "# 30-day rolling volatility\n",
        "rolling_vol = daily_returns.rolling(window=30).std() * np.sqrt(TRADING_DAYS) * 100\n",
        "\n",
        "print('Annualised Volatility (%):')\n",
        "print('=' * 30)\n",
        "for stock in names:\n",
        "    vol = ann_volatility[stock]\n",
        "    bar = '█' * int(vol / 2)\n",
        "    print(f'  {stock:<12}  {vol:5.1f}%  {bar}')\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f'\\n  Nifty 50     {daily_returns.apply(lambda col: col).std().mean() * np.sqrt(TRADING_DAYS) * 100:.1f}%  (approx portfolio avg)')"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "rygKGERL8S1V"
      },
      "source": [
        "### 7.1 — Rolling 30-Day Volatility Chart"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 11,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 549
        },
        "id": "xjTBrniQ8S1V",
        "outputId": "174cf953-1b8b-434d-c5e2-c24d96c8b514"
