        "---\n",
        "## 📋 Section 10 — Key Concepts Reference\n",
        "\n",
        "| Metric | Formula | What it tells you |\n",
        "|--------|---------|-------------------|\n",
        "| **Daily Return** | (P_t − P_{t-1}) / P_{t-1} | % gain/loss each trading day |\n",
        "| **Cumulative Return** | (End Price / Start Price) − 1 | Total % gain over the period |\n",
        "| **Annualised Volatility** | σ_daily × √252 | Risk — how much returns fluctuate per year |\n",
        "| **Sharpe Ratio** | Ann. Return / Ann. Volatility | Return earned per unit of risk taken |\n",
        "| **Drawdown from Peak** | (Current / Peak) − 1 | How far price has fallen from its high |\n",
        "| **Correlation** | Pearson r between return series | How similarly two stocks move |\n",
        "\n",
